<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<!--
    HSK patch: hide the three RN weapon-crafting workbenches from the
    architect menu.

    Buildings affected:
      * RNBench_CQB           — Close Quarters Battle desk
      * RNBench_LBW           — Long Barreled Weapons desk
      * RNBench_HeavyWeapons  — Heavy Weapons desk

    Why hide them?
    All RH2 weapon recipes have been moved to HSK's existing crafting
    workbenches (TableMachining and the gunsmith benches). The original
    RN desks still ship in this mod and were appearing in the architect
    menu, but their internal recipe lists reference the OLD un-converted
    ingredient sets (raw Steel instead of SteelBar, vanilla Components
    instead of HSK ComponentIndustrial, etc.). If the player builds them
    they'll see crafting recipes with broken / inappropriate costs.

    PatchOperationRemove on designationCategory hides each from the build
    UI without deleting the ThingDef itself, so any existing saves that
    reference these benches keep working — they just can't be newly built.
    Same approach we used for the disabled VFE Mechanoids buildings in
    HSK_Disable_Overlap.xml.
-->
<Patch>

    <Operation Class="PatchOperationRemove">
        <xpath>Defs/ThingDef[defName="RNBench_CQB"]/designationCategory</xpath>
    </Operation>

    <Operation Class="PatchOperationRemove">
        <xpath>Defs/ThingDef[defName="RNBench_LBW"]/designationCategory</xpath>
    </Operation>

    <Operation Class="PatchOperationRemove">
        <xpath>Defs/ThingDef[defName="RNBench_HeavyWeapons"]/designationCategory</xpath>
    </Operation>

</Patch>
